data.title: Samantha Stosur
data.meta_description: Samantha Stosur is a tennis player who has competed for Australia. She competed at the 2004, 2008, 2012, 2016, and 2020 Summer Olympic Games.
data.text:
Samantha Stosur is a tennis player who has competed for Australia. She competed at the 2004, 2008, 2012, 2016, and 2020 Summer Olympic Games.
